page.title: 07Square 6
page.content:
The major land use in this square is{Meadowland} which adjoins the river throughout the square. The square also has a tributary to the river. The land in this square is all privately owned by the{Westminster {Estate,}and Houses a{Golf course}and a {Cricket Green. There are no houses in this square, and the Golf course and Cricket Green are both managed by Estate workers from just outside the square.
{Attitudes { }No one lives in this square but members of the Golf club say that the club has a high reputation, with members from all over the county.
